OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few showers through the
OL,6,Fmorning and early afternoon with some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells, but largely
OL,8,Fcloudy. Showers may be wintry at
OL,9,Ftimes. Becoming dry later in the
OL,10,Fafternoon with longer sunny spells
OL,11,Fdeveloping. Winds becoming light later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning cloudy and breezy
OL,14,Fover the Western Isles and Skye with
OL,15,Fshowers at times. Elsewhere will be
OL,16,Fdry and cold with largely clear skies
OL,17,Fleading to a frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
