OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start for many
OL,6,Fit will be a dry day with some long
OL,7,Fspells of sunshine. Turning cloudier
OL,8,Fin the evening with rain spreading
OL,9,Feastwards. Breezy in west.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,13,FSunday and Monday as winds strengthen,
OL,14,Fsome drier and brighter intervals
OL,15,Fpossible. Drier on Tuesday with just
OL,16,Fthe odd shower and sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
